<plot>John and Peg are both deaf and they have a six year old daughter, Lisa. On their way to Peg's parents they have a car accident and John dies. Peg has a nervous breakdown and Peg's mother temporarily takes care of Lisa. But when Peg recovers, her mother won't let her take care of her daughter and files a lawsuit to become Lisa's legal guardian.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?082925</url></doc>
